      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Content structure"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Alinea generates files on your file system in a few places. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "textAlign": "left",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Content is published into a directory as JSON files. Note that "
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "we're considering",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "link",
                      "attrs": {
                        "data-id": "auApxINUu9KWCeMkWjA6S",
                        "data-entry": null,
                        "data-type": null,
                        "href": "https://github.com/alineacms/alinea/issues/10",
                        "target": "_blank",
                        "title": null
                      }
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " making these files more human editable in the future too."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "textAlign": "left",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Media files are published in two places: a JSON file with metadata is placed with the content and the file itself is placed in a separate directory, typically `./public`."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "textAlign": "left",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "A supporting Javascript library is generated inside the `@alinea/generated` package."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "2Yl96Yghl2sIFoaL6JTF1bQCpAO",
      "type": "CodeBlock",
      "code": "// Published content is stored in json files \n// inside the content directory\ncontent\n├ pages // pages root\n│ ├ index.json\n│ ├ blog.json\n│ ╰ blog\n│   ├ blog-post.json\n│   ╰ another-blog-post.json\n╰ media // media root\n  ├ image.json\n  ╰ file.json\n\n// A folder which is publicly available\npublic\n├ image.XYZ.png\n╰ file.XYZ.pdf\n\n// The alinea directory exports a Javascript library\n// which can be imported from @alinea/generated\nnode_modules/@alinea/generated\n├ ...\n├ config.js\n╰ store.js",
